marker.placeholder: .desc Gauge has many repositories, all on GitHub. Gauge core is written in Golang. Gauge also has a rich plugin repository, and not everything in there is in Golang. If this is the kind of thing you like, then you can pick up any pending feature/bug, simple or complex. Just make sure you write a test and send us a pull request.
